♪That we shall do what we can wherever we go♪

22
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:40,900
♪Together, another journey awaits♪

23
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:50,020
[The Blood of Youth]

24
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:52,970
[Episode 10]

25
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:54,340
Come forth!

26
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,900
What's wrong with my Tingyu Sword?

27
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:10,780
You...

28
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:11,900
I knew you were a wo...

29
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:16,260
woman.

30
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:19,060
But that doesn't do you justice.

31
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:21,580
You're like a fairy.

32
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:35,540
I will return three months later

33
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:37,420
for another challenge.

34
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:44,740
(Her voice is soothing too.)

35
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:52,500
From now on,

36
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:53,780
I'll call you Peach Blossom.

37
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:05,820
(And after that,)

38
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:08,300
(Zhao Yuzhen)

39
00:03:08,380 --> 00:03:09,420
(waited by the peach blossom tree)

40
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,020
(for three months.)

41
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:13,700
(From winter to spring,)

42
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:15,100
(until the peach blossom blooms again.)

43
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:18,220
(No need to use the Fire Formation Secret Arts)

44
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:19,820
(and he could have big, plump,)

45
00:03:19,820 --> 00:03:20,940
(sweet peaches soon.)

46
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:28,340
(However...)

47
00:03:28,340 --> 00:03:29,340
[Peach Blossom]

48
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:30,300
(The one who promised)

49
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:31,100
(she would return after three months)

50
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:33,980
(did not come at all.)

51
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,380
Master said

52
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:39,700
all beautiful people lie.

53
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:41,740
It seems like it's true.

54
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:45,340
I guess waiting for peaches is more realistic.

55
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:47,300
Hey, dummy.

56
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:49,340
Waiting for peaches?

57
00:03:51,540 --> 00:03:52,180
You're late.

58
00:03:56,700 --> 00:03:57,700
I went to search for this sword,

59
00:03:59,020 --> 00:03:59,900
so I was late for seven days.

60
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:01,460
Oh, Iron Glacier

61
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:02,420
from the Records of Famous Swords.

62
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:04,500
A fine sword you have there.

63
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,020
Oh, my dear fairy.

64
00:04:06,740 --> 00:04:07,780
Why are you wearing a mask again?

65
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:09,380
It doesn't look good on you.

66
00:04:10,580 --> 00:04:11,500
Taking it off

67
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:12,660
is better.

68
00:04:14,340 --> 00:04:15,220
Talkative.

69
00:04:30,060 --> 00:04:30,620
Zhao Yuzhen.

70
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:32,020
What is that technique?

71
00:04:32,580 --> 00:04:33,900
The secret technique of Mount Wangcheng,

72
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:35,220
Supreme Dragon Elephant Skill.

73
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:37,340
Why don't you use your sword?

74
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:38,580
Supreme Dragon Elephant Skill

75
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:40,300
is the strongest technique of Mount Wangcheng.

76
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:42,020
It is as good as, if not better than,
the Infinite Sword Technique.

77
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,420
I don't care.

78
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:44,820
Unsheathe your sword now.

79
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:46,500
Only if you take off

80
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:46,900
your mask.

81
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:47,900
You...

82
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:06,260
Satisfied?

83
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:07,740
Now, draw your sword.

84
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:10,820
Peach Blossom.

85
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:24,380
Creation and destruction

86
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:25,540
are all a tribulation.

87
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:27,540
And before the coming of life,

88
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:29,380
infinite tribulations have taken place.

89
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:37,260
♪Deep inside the clouds♪

90
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:41,100
♪I hear the whispering of your zither music♪

91
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:43,740
Zhao Yuzhen.

92
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:45,580
What is that sword technique?

93
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:47,220
Infinite Sword for infinite tribulations.

94
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:48,900
Those who are caught in it

95
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:50,020
will suffer

96
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:50,940
for an eternity.

97
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:51,900
Sure.

98
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:53,540
Just as the infinity in its name suggests.

99
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:54,980
I too have my technique.

100
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:58,980
♪The candlelight flickers
as you dance among the flower petals♪

101
00:06:00,940 --> 00:06:03,660
♪Let the snow fills the sky♪

102
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:08,060
♪Eating away at the time♪

103
00:06:08,780 --> 00:06:10,180
Beautiful Day!

104
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:12,580
♪Alas, one thought is all it takes to reunite♪

105
00:06:12,940 --> 00:06:14,300
♪One thought is all it takes to part♪

106
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:16,780
♪I can't endure this life of tribulations♪

107
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,180
How beautiful.

108
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:20,180
♪The beautiful seasons♪

109
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:21,700
Charge!

110
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:23,860
Sure.

111
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:24,860
Here I come.

112
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:28,380
♪Are just our fates intertwined♪

113
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:33,820
♪A romance and an obsession♪

114
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:38,300
♪Tears can't move my thoughts away
from whatever they are so focused on♪

115
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:39,860
♪Deep love doesn't last long♪

116
00:06:40,020 --> 00:06:44,540
♪Who to say goodbye to?♪

117
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:51,580
♪A lifetime of longing for the love
of half a lifetime♪

118
00:06:51,860 --> 00:06:55,180
♪The season will never grow old,
and this love will last forever♪

119
