♪When all at once I turn my head♪

128
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:38,060
♪I find you there
where lantern light is dimly shed♪

129
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:41,820
♪When all at once I turn my head♪

130
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:49,500
♪I find you there
where lantern light is dimly shed♪

131
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:50,020
-You...
-You...

132
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:51,940
Go ahead.

133
00:07:52,940 --> 00:07:53,380
Little fairy.

134
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:55,140
You are beautiful,

135
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:56,740
so why do you hide your face

136
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:57,860
under a mask?

137
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:00,020
You are strong,

138
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:01,900
so why don't you leave the mountain
and have an adventure?

139
00:08:04,140 --> 00:08:04,740
My master told me

140
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:06,260
that if I leave the mountain,

141
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:07,620
many people will die.

142
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:09,580
When I come here the third time,

143
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:10,620
you will come with me

144
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:12,380
and leave the mountain.

145
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:17,100
I...

146
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:18,980
I have to get my martial uncle's permission.

147
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:21,460
How strong is your martial uncle?

148
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:23,300
Stronger than me.

149
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:24,860
But it might not be the case

150
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,460
after a year.

151
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:28,740
Then I will be back here after one year.

152
00:08:29,540 --> 00:08:30,500
If he won't let you go,

153
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:32,500
I'll fight him until he does.

154
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:37,100
We protected him for 16 years,

155
00:08:38,020 --> 00:08:39,700
but he still can't escape the mortal pursuits.

156
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:43,420
[Lyu Suzhen, Mount Wangcheng]
[Yin Changsong, Mount Wangcheng]

157
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:45,140
Master told me all that.

158
00:08:45,820 --> 00:08:46,500
And then,

159
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:48,100
he passed out.

160
00:08:49,180 --> 00:08:50,020
After that,

161
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:52,180
my second master also visited

162
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:53,060
Mount Wangcheng.

163
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:54,660
Just right after your martial uncle,

164
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:55,620
Lei Yunhe, visited it.

165
00:08:57,020 --> 00:08:58,940
I don't know about the details,

166
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:01,220
but if you want to know,

167
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:03,220
you can ask Second Master.

168
00:09:04,380 --> 00:09:05,860
I don't dare to.

169
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:07,060
Oh, right.

170
00:09:07,580 --> 00:09:08,700
I'm in Xueyue City

171
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:10,580
for a while now,

172
00:09:11,380 --> 00:09:12,100
but why haven't I met

173
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:12,940
the Principal City Lord,

174
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:14,140
Baili Dongjun?

175
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:15,460
You have.

176
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:16,900
Have I?

177
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:18,820
When?

178
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:20,260
Not only have you met him,

179
00:09:20,820 --> 00:09:21,940
but you've also had Beauty of Four Seasons liquor

180
00:09:21,940 --> 00:09:22,940
(that he made too.)

181
00:09:26,420 --> 00:09:27,340
That's him?

182
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:29,820
I have to thank him

183
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,060
when I see him next time.

184
00:09:31,580 --> 00:09:32,060
Come on.

185
00:09:32,410 --> 00:09:33,060
Drink.

186
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:42,660
Oh.

187
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:44,300
I have another question.

188
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:46,820
Why can't Zhao Yuzhen

189
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:47,980
leave the mountain?

190
00:09:49,540 --> 00:09:50,860
There are many rumors

191
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:51,780
about Zhao Yuzhen.

192
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:54,060
When he was born,

193
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:56,540
a ray of sun shone into the room.

194
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:58,820
The Senior Celestial Master of Mount Wangcheng

195
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:00,180
came to receive him in person

196
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:02,340
because Zhao Yuzhen
is the reincarnation of a deity.

197
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:05,700
He then brought Zhao Yuzhen
back to Mount Wangcheng.

198
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:08,420
Zhao Yuzhen stayed there since then.

199
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:10,420
They say Zhao Yuzhen

200
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:11,420
can't leave the mountain

201
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:12,620
because of a prophecy

202
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:14,060
by the Senior Celestial Master, Lyu Suzhen.

203
00:10:14,740 --> 00:10:16,050
Apparently, if he leaves the mountain,

204
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,020
it will bring unrest.

205
00:10:18,740 --> 00:10:21,300
It might even become a threat
to a certain someone

206
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:22,500
in Tianqi City.

207
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:29,940
Therefore, 5,000 Iron Troops are stationed

208
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:32,140
30 li away from Mount Wangcheng.

209
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:34,300
Just in case Zhao Yuzhen leaves the mountain.

210
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:36,620
Some also say

211
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:37,540
that Zhao Yuzhen

212
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:38,860
contains the fate

213
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,540
of Mount Wangcheng.

214
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:42,020
But the prophecy

215
00:10:42,220 --> 00:10:43,460
is most likely fictional.

216
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:45,380
They're just worried that he won't come back.

217
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:47,460
So with his power,

218
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:48,700
no one can stop him

219
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:50,500
as long as he wants to leave?

220
00:10:51,180 --> 00:10:52,940
For a decade, he hardly leaves

221
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,820
his courtyard,

222
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:56,900
let alone the mountain.

223
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,380
I think he's waiting for someone.

224
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:01,220
If that person doesn't show up,

225
00:11:01,740 --> 00:11:03,100
I think he'll keep waiting.

226
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:11,020
Something's on your mind.

227
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:20,460
I was born to the Tang Clan.

228
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:22,140
I am a disciple

229
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:23,180
of Tang Lianyue, an elder of the Tang Clan.

230
00:11:24,180 --> 00:11:25,500
I thought I would live and die

231
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:26,660
for the Tang Clan,

232
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:29,220
but I was sent to Xueyue City out of a sudden.

233
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:31,620
And now, I'm a disciple

234
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:32,860
of the Liquor Deity, Baili Dongjun.

235
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:35,420
Master Lianyue told me

236
00:11:36,180 --> 00:11:37,380
to wait for someone here.

237
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:41,180
And I have waited for six years.

238
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:45,620
The Tang Clan always does this.

239
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,540
All of you were born

240
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:49,980
with countless duties and responsibilities.

241
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:52,740
So you lead a life of burdens.

242
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:55,140
You have to meddle in Xueyue City's affairs

243
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:57,540
while performing the duty your clan gave you.

244
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:00,580
People try to live

245
00:12:01,380 --> 00:12:02,300
every day too,

246
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:03,660
but they live

247
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:04,740
for themselves.

248
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,820
They don't have that many other things
to worry about.

249
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:12,220
Are you sure you're here in Xueyue City

250
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:13,860
for money alone?

251
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:16,100
Money

252
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:17,660
is important.

253
00:12:19,740 --> 00:12:20,460
Eight hundred taels.

254
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:22,100
It sure is important then.

255
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:23,180
You're wrong.

256
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:25,980
It's eight million taels.

257
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:31,980
If you had that much money,

258
00:12:32,140 --> 00:12:32,860
what would you do?

259
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:40,420
Assemble an army

260
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:43,780
and raze Tianqi City to the ground.

261
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:49,460
I'll join you.

262
00:12:50,140 --> 00:12:51,020
Why?

263
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:52,980
You came to Xueyue City with me.

264
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:54,420
So I'll go to Tianqi City with you.

265
00:12:58,300 --> 00:12:58,820
Sure.

266
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:08,940
You're not

267
00:13:09,020 --> 00:13:09,860
the person I'm waiting for?

268
00:13:11,460 --> 00:13:12,100
Why is a man

269
00:13:12,300 --> 00:13:13,140
waiting for another man?

270
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,220
Don't speak to your senior like that.

271
00:13:15,580 --> 00:13:16,700
I will beat you up.

272
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:18,700
You're just taking advantage

273
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:19,620
of my lack of martial skills.

274
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,100
Do you want a fair fight with something else?

275
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,020
Sure.

276
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:23,420
Try me.

277
00:13:24,620 --> 00:13:25,780
You're a disciple of Liquor Deity.

278
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:27,660
So let's compete with our alcohol tolerance.

279
00:13:27,980 --> 00:13:28,540
Sure.

280
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:30,620
I'll get some liquor here.

281
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:33,820
Come on.

282
00:13:41,620 --> 00:13:44,620
[Mount Wangcheng]

283
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:54,860
Mount Wangcheng.

284
00:13:57,660 --> 00:13:58,300
The elders are discussing

285
00:13:58,500 --> 00:13:59,500
