286
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:00,420
Let them be.

287
00:14:00,660 --> 00:14:01,220
I must practice my sword skill

288
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:02,420
and become a sword deity.

289
00:14:03,620 --> 00:14:04,860
Hong, I know you are headstrong

290
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:06,380
and I'm not here to persuade you.

291
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:08,140
But tell me,

292
00:14:08,660 --> 00:14:09,580
why are you doing this?

293
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:17,060
Because I saw it

294
00:14:19,180 --> 00:14:19,860
on Mount Wangcheng.

295
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:24,740
What is that?

296
00:14:25,300 --> 00:14:25,900
No sword aura

297
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:27,100
can be this powerful.

298
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:39,820
Miss.

299
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:42,700
You

300
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:44,340
did that?

301
00:14:45,620 --> 00:14:46,300
Yes. So?

302
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:47,780
Nothing.

303
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:49,220
No.

304
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:50,420
It's not nothing.

305
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:51,580
You... You...

306
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:55,580
Miss.

307
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:57,060
I'm Lei Hong.

308
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:01,940
The beauty of that slash.

309
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:04,300
Mount Wangcheng?

310
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:07,900
[Mount Wangcheng]
Who's there?

311
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:09,900
How dare you venture into Mount Wangcheng?

312
00:15:10,420 --> 00:15:11,340
I'm Lei Yunhe

313
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:12,860
from Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect.

314
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:14,500
I'm here to scale the mountain.

315
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:15,940
Zhao Yuzhen.

316
00:15:16,370 --> 00:15:17,100
Come out now.

317
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:18,020
In your dreams!

318
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:19,540
Thunderclap Finger.

319
00:15:21,020 --> 00:15:21,900
Purge!

320
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:39,020
My friend saw your technique

321
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:40,980
and he said the sword is the most beautiful

322
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:42,060
of all martial arts.

323
00:15:43,300 --> 00:15:44,300
I'd like to see if it's true.

324
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,260
Zhao Yuzhen.

325
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:01,380
I am here again.

326
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:03,500
I am Lei Yunhe

327
00:16:04,100 --> 00:16:06,180
from Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect.
I'm here to scale the mountain.

328
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:12,980
The spring moon illuminates the courtyard.

329
00:16:15,620 --> 00:16:17,420
The silver light waltzes on the cup of wine.

330
00:16:18,980 --> 00:16:20,100
As I traverse the corridor,

331
00:16:21,020 --> 00:16:23,180
a waft of the half-fallen plum blossom
enters my nose.

332
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:26,100
Under the misty moon

333
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:30,220
is where the youngsters entertain themselves.

334
00:16:31,780 --> 00:16:32,940
Unlike the autumn moon

335
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:37,660
that guides lost souls.

336
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:48,220
This is the last pot.

337
00:16:53,580 --> 00:16:54,660
You won, Lian.

338
00:16:55,860 --> 00:16:56,940
Come on, Lian.

339
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:00,740
Lian?

340
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:02,020
Lian?

341
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:05,500
Wow.

342
00:17:05,940 --> 00:17:07,220
He passed out while seated.

343
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:12,700
Oh, I forgot to inquire about the lady in green.

344
00:17:17,940 --> 00:17:19,140
Someone sneaked into Xueyue City at night.

345
00:17:22,540 --> 00:17:23,660
That's where Master is training!

346
00:17:29,740 --> 00:17:30,340
Who are you?

347
00:17:31,260 --> 00:17:32,580
I should ask you that question.

348
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:34,500
I can tell you my name,

349
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:36,060
but do you have the guts to hear it?

350
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:38,060
My master is training in solitude.

351
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:39,660
No one is to disturb her.

352
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:40,900
Please return after a few days

353
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:41,860
if you want to see her.

354
00:17:42,420 --> 00:17:43,220
After two days,

355
00:17:43,580 --> 00:17:45,380
I won't stop you if you come here.

356
00:17:48,380 --> 00:17:49,980
So you are a disciple of Li Hanyi.

357
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:52,740
She has a disciple now?

358
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:55,980
What is your name?

359
00:17:58,100 --> 00:17:59,140
Lei Wujie.

360
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:02,620
Okay.

361
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:03,780
Move aside now.

362
00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:05,180
I have to see Li Hanyi.

363
00:18:05,660 --> 00:18:06,660
Don't waste my time.

364
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:08,260
I just said

365
00:18:08,700 --> 00:18:10,100
she is busy training now.

366
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:11,580
I may not be strong,

367
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:12,820
but I can't let you

368
00:18:12,980 --> 00:18:13,780
enter like this either.

369
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:15,260
Ridiculous.

370
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:17,060
You can't stop me.

371
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:25,420
Fire Infusion from the Lei Clan.

372
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:27,500
And Wushuang Fist.

373
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:29,100
Not bad.

374
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:30,780
Who are you?

375
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:32,500
Why did you enter Xueyue City at night?

376
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:38,500
Do you know this sword?

377
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:40,740
It's a broken sword.

378
00:18:42,380 --> 00:18:43,420
Li Hanyi

379
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,980
broke my sword.

380
00:18:46,940 --> 00:18:48,740
Its name is Severance.

381
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:51,460
One slash to sever the water

382
00:18:52,260 --> 00:18:53,420
and a thousand rivers change their course.

383
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:56,700
You're the City Lord of Wushuang City, Song Yanhui.

384
00:18:57,220 --> 00:18:58,500
[Song Yanhui, Wushuang City]

385
00:18:59,940 --> 00:19:00,900
Is Wushuang City invading

386
00:19:00,900 --> 00:19:01,780
Xueyue City now?

387
00:19:04,060 --> 00:19:05,140
What are you on about, brat?

388
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:07,100
I'm here to test my sword with your master.

389
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:08,820
I don't have time for you.

390
00:19:09,300 --> 00:19:10,060
Move aside.

391
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:11,900
City Lord Song, if you want to enter,

392
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:15,220
you'll have to fight me.

393
00:19:15,580 --> 00:19:16,580
You're not worth

394
00:19:17,540 --> 00:19:18,620
my time.

395
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:31,140
Let go of me.

396
00:19:31,380 --> 00:19:32,060
Like I said,

397
00:19:32,940 --> 00:19:34,180
as long as I still live,

398
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:36,140
you can't enter.

399
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:52,980
Tingyu.

400
00:20:00,100 --> 00:20:01,740
Find the reason to draw your sword.

401
00:20:04,020 --> 00:20:05,500
(The reason to draw my sword...)

402
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:17,420
Sword Art.

403
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:19,700
I too have my technique.

404
00:20:27,540 --> 00:20:28,060
Sword Art,

405
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:30,180
Beautiful Day.

406
00:20:30,660 --> 00:20:31,820
Beautiful Day.

407
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:36,340
A technique by Xueyue Sword Deity, Li Hanyi.

408
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:42,260
Please enlighten me, City Lord Song.

409
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:46,500
It is beautiful.

410
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:48,860
You are now worth my time.

411
00:21:06,540 --> 00:21:07,100
Master.

412
00:21:09,420 --> 00:21:10,620
The Beautiful Day passed down

413
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:12,020
by a sword deity, you said?

414
00:21:13,380 --> 00:21:14,100
When did I ever teach you

415
00:21:14,100 --> 00:21:15,140
a lousy technique like that?

416
00:21:16,740 --> 00:21:17,580
If this gets out,

417
00:21:18,340 --> 00:21:19,460
it will make me

418
00:21:20,020 --> 00:21:21,220
look very bad.

419
00:21:24,660 --> 00:21:25,340
Master,

420
00:21:25,980 --> 00:21:27,620
I now have a reason to draw my sword.

421
00:21:31,740 --> 00:21:33,020
If that is enough to make you

422
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:34,300
this elated,

423
00:21:35,580 --> 00:21:36,380
how am I supposed to teach you

424
00:21:36,540 --> 00:21:37,460
even stronger techniques?

425
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:44,780
He drew his sword to protect someone.

426
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:46,780
You found yourself a good disciple.

427
00:21:47,980 --> 00:21:48,660
Why does it

428
00:21:50,060 --> 00:21:51,020
always come to this?

429
00:22:00,980 --> 00:22:02,380
I heard you have found a disciple too.

430
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:04,500
He managed to unlock the Wushuang Sword Box

431
00:22:05,340 --> 00:22:07,300
and is training to command the 13 swords.

432
00:22:07,980 --> 00:22:08,900
My disciple

433
00:22:09,620 --> 00:22:11,060
is far more talented than I am.

434
00:22:11,820 --> 00:22:12,740
Within five years,

435
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:14,300
he'll become a sword deity.

436
00:22:16,260 --> 00:22:16,700
Sure.

437
00:22:17,620 --> 00:22:18,300
Five years.

438
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:21,380
Within three years, my disciple

439
00:22:22,100 --> 00:22:23,100
will become a sword deity.

440
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:25,620
As confident as always.

441
00:22:26,260 --> 00:22:26,940
Song Yanhui,

442
00:22:27,620 --> 00:22:29,100
you sparred with me thrice

443
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:30,580
and you failed thrice.

444
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:32,900
Today

445
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:36,300
will be your final attempt.

446
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:37,900
After today,

447
00:22:38,500 --> 00:22:39,660
you will stop hoping

448
00:22:40,780 --> 00:22:41,980
that you can surpass me.

449
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:44,340
Bring it on.

450
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:53,940
Third City Lord.

451
00:22:57,540 --> 00:22:58,140
Luoxia.

452
00:22:58,500 --> 00:23:00,380
Have you seen what a sword deity is like
when he is mad?

453
00:23:02,140 --> 00:23:03,500
They say a sword deity is above emotion.

454
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:04,420
They don't experience happiness, rage,

455
00:23:04,460 --> 00:23:05,100
sadness, or sorrow.

456
00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:07,300
Other than the Wrathful Sword Deity

457
00:23:07,300 --> 00:23:08,060
who made a name with his imposing aura,

458
00:23:09,140 --> 00:23:09,980
other sword deities

459
00:23:10,340 --> 00:23:11,780
don't get angry easily.

460
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:13,700
They don't

461
00:23:14,380 --> 00:23:15,820
because if they do,

462
00:23:15,820 --> 00:23:17,260
the world will be sundered.

463
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:19,860
Hanyi is angry now.

464
00:23:20,580 --> 00:23:21,980
Song Yanhui hurt Lei Wujie?

465
00:23:24,180 --> 00:23:25,780
Lei Wujie managed to unsheathe Tingyu Sword

466
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:27,460
but for the reason Hanyi

467
00:23:27,820 --> 00:23:28,700
fears the most.

468
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:30,820
Luoxia.

469
00:23:31,540 --> 00:23:33,100
Song Yanhui and you

470
00:23:33,260 --> 00:23:34,020
have a history

471
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:35,900
in Canglan River, don't you?

472
00:23:36,180 --> 00:23:37,180
Go save him.

473
00:23:37,740 --> 00:23:38,460
Otherwise,

474
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:39,540
the City Lord

475
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:41,260
of Wushuang City

476
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,740
will die in Xueyue City.

477
00:23:55,940 --> 00:23:56,980
Any regrets for dying

478
00:23:58,100 --> 00:23:58,980
under my sword?

479
00:23:59,780 --> 00:24:00,660
None

480
00:24:01,540 --> 00:24:02,500
at all.

481
00:24:03,180 --> 00:24:04,500
You're weighed down by your duty.

482
00:24:06,140 --> 00:24:07,700
If you weren't the City Lord of Wushuang City,

483
00:24:09,220 --> 00:24:10,660
you would have reached a greater height.

484
00:24:17,380 --> 00:24:18,180
Please spare him.

485
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:24,860
Why?

486
00:24:25,300 --> 00:24:26,220
You already failed thrice.

487
00:24:26,780 --> 00:24:27,500
Why do you have to do this again?

488
00:24:27,980 --> 00:24:28,740
Give up already.

489
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:36,100
You drew your sword

490
00:24:36,860 --> 00:24:37,820
to protect others.

491
00:24:39,620 --> 00:24:40,100
I hate

492
00:24:40,260 --> 00:24:41,500
to see this,

493
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:44,500
but I see why.

494
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:47,380
Because your father is Lei

495
00:24:48,820 --> 00:24:49,860
and your mother is Li.

496
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:53,180
I'll accept this.

497
00:24:57,460 --> 00:24:57,940
You...

498
00:24:58,460 --> 00:25:00,100
[Luoxia]
Why are you in Xueyue City?

499
00:25:00,660 --> 00:25:01,180
Stop moving.

500
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:04,740
And don't play dumb.

501
00:25:05,220 --> 00:25:05,980
You know very well

502
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:06,740
I'm in Xueyue City.

503
00:25:09,140 --> 00:25:09,980
Whether you're here or not,

504
00:25:11,100 --> 00:25:12,100
what difference does it make?

505
00:25:13,060 --> 00:25:13,860
Whether you win or not,

506
00:25:14,540 --> 00:25:15,380
what difference does it make?

507
00:25:17,820 --> 00:25:18,900
I have a disciple now.

508
00:25:19,900 --> 00:25:22,060
His vast potential

509
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:23,540
is second to none.

510
00:25:24,740 --> 00:25:27,140
I'm sure he can restore

511
00:25:27,300 --> 00:25:28,700
Wushuang City to its former glory.

512
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:30,620
I lost,

513
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:32,460
but my disciple

514
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:33,660
won't.

515
00:25:37,940 --> 00:25:38,740
Is restoring Wushuang City's former glory

516
00:25:39,820 --> 00:25:40,700
that important?

517
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:42,700
Is defeating Xueyue Sword Deity

518
00:25:44,100 --> 00:25:44,940
that important?

519
00:25:46,540 --> 00:25:47,260
What about me?

520
00:25:48,020 --> 00:25:48,940
Am I not important?

521
00:25:50,540 --> 00:25:50,780
Yes.

522
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:52,180
Sorry.

523
00:25:55,380 --> 00:25:56,260
You deserve a beating.

524
00:25:56,540 --> 00:25:57,020
You...

525
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:58,020
What?

526
00:25:58,780 --> 00:25:59,860
I just want to hit you.

527
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:00,740
Rascal.

528
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:01,740
Do you know who I am?

529
00:26:02,060 --> 00:26:02,740
Why should I care?

530
00:26:03,100 --> 00:26:04,060
You bullied my master.

531
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:04,900
I swear

532
00:26:04,980 --> 00:26:05,660
with my name

533
00:26:05,900 --> 00:26:06,940
that you will leave this place bruised.

534
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:10,860
Master.

535
00:26:11,060 --> 00:26:11,780
Once I have him,

536
00:26:12,100 --> 00:26:12,940
I'll castrate him for you.

537
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:20,820
Come again

538
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:22,620
and I'll hit you again.

539
00:26:34,540 --> 00:26:35,740
Master, you lost again.

540
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:37,420
Yeah.

541
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,740
I lost thoroughly.

542
00:26:40,460 --> 00:26:41,860
Li Hanyi and I

543
00:26:42,140 --> 00:26:43,580
are several leagues

544
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:44,380
apart.

545
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:45,940
From now on,

546
00:26:46,820 --> 00:26:48,500
I won't spar with her in Xueyue City

547
00:26:48,900 --> 00:26:49,860
anymore.

548
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:52,980
It's okay.

549
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:55,380
I'll win on your behalf.

550
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:02,380
I met someone this time.

551
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:04,740
His name is Lei Wujie.

552
00:27:06,420 --> 00:27:07,140
I'm Lei Wujie of the Lei family

553
00:27:07,420 --> 00:27:08,540
from Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect.

554
00:27:09,420 --> 00:27:10,780
Never heard of you.

555
00:27:12,020 --> 00:27:13,260
You will.

556
00:27:14,060 --> 00:27:15,340
It's rare to see

557
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:16,540
that you actually

558
00:27:16,660 --> 00:27:17,780
remember someone's name.

559
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:20,380
Because he's unique.

560
00:27:21,380 --> 00:27:22,300
Just like everyone I met

561
00:27:23,100 --> 00:27:23,820
on that day.

562
00:27:24,540 --> 00:27:25,820
I remember their faces.

563
00:27:26,780 --> 00:27:28,380
He is a disciple of Li Hanyi now.

564
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:30,980
I tested his skills.

565
00:27:31,660 --> 00:27:32,580
He's still

566
00:27:33,300 --> 00:27:34,380
quite inferior to you.

567
00:27:35,260 --> 00:27:36,380
I told Li Hanyi

568
00:27:37,180 --> 00:27:38,060
that you

569
00:27:39,180 --> 00:27:41,300
would become a sword deity within five years.

570
00:27:42,140 --> 00:27:43,060
But she said

571
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:45,580
Lei Wujie only needs three years.

572
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:49,140
It seems like she has high expectations

573
00:27:49,340 --> 00:27:50,660
of her disciple.

574
00:28:06,940 --> 00:28:07,620
You can command

575
00:28:07,780 --> 00:28:08,540
ten swords now.

576
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:09,780
