577
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:12,260
If Lei Wujie can become a sword deity
within three years,

578
00:28:12,620 --> 00:28:14,020
then I'll do it within a year.

579
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:16,500
Go forth.

580
00:28:25,500 --> 00:28:25,940
Withdraw!

581
00:28:46,220 --> 00:28:48,780
