582
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:50,580
back to its prime.

583
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:52,380
Master.

584
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:53,620
I don't want to be

585
00:28:53,780 --> 00:28:54,900
the City Lord of Wushuang City.

586
00:28:55,420 --> 00:28:56,780
I just enjoy training with my swords.

587
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:59,500
But if that's your wish,

588
00:29:00,380 --> 00:29:01,580
I'll do it.

589
00:29:07,980 --> 00:29:08,460
All right.

590
00:29:08,980 --> 00:29:10,140
Come back to Wushuang City with me.

591
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:18,900
He is Song Yanhui?

592
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:21,380
I hit the City Lord of Wushuang City?

593
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,420
He is Song Yanhui?

594
00:29:23,500 --> 00:29:25,020
I hit the City Lord of Wushuang City?

595
00:29:25,940 --> 00:29:26,860
My goodness.

596
00:29:29,500 --> 00:29:30,060
Oh no.

597
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:33,420
Oh no.

598
00:29:34,020 --> 00:29:34,740
What should I do?

599
00:29:36,500 --> 00:29:37,220
Where's your master?

600
00:29:44,380 --> 00:29:45,180
Song Yanhui has left?

601
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:47,500
Last night, yes.

602
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:53,020
You still wear that mask

603
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:54,260
