608
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:12,580
That's amusing.

609
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:14,900
If you care about him,

610
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:17,460
why don't you return to Wushuang City with him?

611
00:30:18,700 --> 00:30:20,100
I am not his priority.

612
00:30:21,580 --> 00:30:22,620
It doesn't matter if I'm there or not.

613
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:26,380
Yesterday, I...

614
00:30:28,860 --> 00:30:29,780
How is Lei Wujie?

615
00:30:30,220 --> 00:30:30,900
