617
00:30:33,540 --> 00:30:34,620
He just needs a few days' rest.

618
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:37,660
When do you plan

619
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:38,340
to tell Lei Wujie

620
00:30:38,540 --> 00:30:39,540
who you are to him?

621
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:46,140
