630
00:31:05,260 --> 00:31:06,100
I am not

631
00:31:07,020 --> 00:31:08,300
a good sister.

632
00:31:11,740 --> 00:31:13,020
But I'm happy

633
00:31:14,180 --> 00:31:15,220
