636
00:31:19,420 --> 00:31:20,060
When I told you

637
00:31:20,140 --> 00:31:21,100
to go to see Zhao Yuzhen,

638
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:22,580
you said the same thing.

639
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:27,580
