644
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:46,540
With the aid of our celestial masters,

645
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:47,860
he regained consciousness.

646
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:50,900
But it'll be a while

647
00:31:51,380 --> 00:31:52,620
before he can make a full recovery.

648
00:31:53,340 --> 00:31:54,140
Does that mean

649
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:55,380
he cannot see

650
00:31:55,420 --> 00:31:56,460
any visitors for the next few days?

651
00:31:57,300 --> 00:31:58,060
Master says

652
00:31:58,540 --> 00:31:59,420
that if someone disturbs him,

653
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:00,700
he might

654
00:32:00,780 --> 00:32:01,860
go rogue again.

655
00:32:04,020 --> 00:32:05,900
[Mount Wangcheng]

656
00:32:08,340 --> 00:32:08,860
All right then.

657
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:10,460
Please ask Master Lyu

658
00:32:10,860 --> 00:32:11,740
to tell him

659
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:13,020
that I was here.

660
00:32:22,740 --> 00:32:23,740
I guess it's good

661
00:32:24,860 --> 00:32:25,780
for both of us.

662
00:32:26,580 --> 00:32:27,180
You're just

663
00:32:27,380 --> 00:32:28,260
like Song Yanhui.

664
00:32:29,140 --> 00:32:30,100
I would hit you

665
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:31,460
if you weren't stronger than me.

666
00:32:32,380 --> 00:32:33,300
Just unbelievable.

667
00:32:46,740 --> 00:32:47,940
I can finally wield

668
00:32:48,140 --> 00:32:49,700
Tingyu Sword now.

669
00:32:53,220 --> 00:32:54,100
However...

670
00:32:56,380 --> 00:32:57,060
No.

671
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:58,940
You don't unsheathe it with your strength.

672
00:33:00,740 --> 00:33:02,620
Something feels off.

673
00:33:03,180 --> 00:33:05,780
It's like something is missing.

674
00:33:13,420 --> 00:33:13,980
Xiao Se!

675
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:14,900
Lian!

676
00:33:19,220 --> 00:33:20,380
How do you know we will be here?

677
00:33:21,180 --> 00:33:22,300
It seems like you have mastered

678
00:33:22,500 --> 00:33:24,140
the First Level of Stillwater Sword.

679
00:33:25,060 --> 00:33:25,780
Unlike someone I know

680
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:27,260
whose fleeing skill

681
00:33:27,660 --> 00:33:28,580
just keeps improving.

682
00:33:30,300 --> 00:33:30,900
Lian.

683
00:33:31,620 --> 00:33:32,090
Will you

684
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:34,500
fight me?

685
00:33:36,820 --> 00:33:37,460
Sure.

686
00:33:54,900 --> 00:33:55,340
This sword

687
00:33:56,100 --> 00:33:57,300
was given to me by Xueyue Sword Deity.

688
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,420
Beautiful Day!

689
00:34:26,860 --> 00:34:28,060
That's your Beautiful Day?

690
00:34:28,740 --> 00:34:29,740
Do you have Second Master's approval?

691
00:34:30,580 --> 00:34:31,180
Lian.

692
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:33,380
Please don't tell my master.

693
00:34:33,980 --> 00:34:35,180
I've been practicing with her

694
00:34:35,540 --> 00:34:36,340
and if I ever make a mistake,

695
00:34:36,940 --> 00:34:38,300
she hits me on my head.

696
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:39,500
(Wrong.)

697
00:34:41,620 --> 00:34:42,260
Jie.

698
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:43,820
How many times have I told you?

699
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,580
When you thrust, the sword has to be horizontal.

700
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:47,580
That wasn't Sancai Sword Technique at all.

701
00:34:51,380 --> 00:34:51,860
Jie.

702
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:54,180
Stop crying.

703
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:55,860
I'll buy you tanghulu,
(*sugar-coated hawthorn)

704
00:34:55,860 --> 00:34:56,540
all right?

705
00:35:01,580 --> 00:35:02,100
Lei Wujie?

706
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:03,900
Lei Wujie?

707
00:35:04,420 --> 00:35:05,700
Snap back, dummy.

708
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:08,060
Sorry.

709
00:35:08,740 --> 00:35:09,900
It's just

710
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:11,580
that when Master hits me,

711
00:35:11,980 --> 00:35:12,940
it feels quite familiar.

712
00:35:13,660 --> 00:35:14,900
You're indeed a dummy.

713
00:35:15,380 --> 00:35:16,340
It hurt a lot when you were hit.

714
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:17,780
But now, you reminisce about the moment

715
00:35:17,820 --> 00:35:18,700
when you were hit.

716
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:21,180
Oh, right.

717
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:22,580
Where is the Second Master?

718
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:24,340
She trains with her sword

719
00:35:24,340 --> 00:35:25,100
in the mountain every day.

720
00:35:25,540 --> 00:35:26,260
In the morning,

721
00:35:26,500 --> 00:35:27,620
she'll supervise my training.

722
00:35:28,100 --> 00:35:29,420
But after that, she's gone.

723
00:35:30,380 --> 00:35:31,940
When it's time to eat,

724
00:35:32,250 --> 00:35:33,660
she appears again. On time too.

725
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:35,780
Do I hear a complaint?

726
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:37,780
Of course not.

727
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:40,420
I'm just thinking

728
00:35:40,980 --> 00:35:42,260
that if one day I quit martial arts,

729
00:35:42,900 --> 00:35:44,460
I will leave the mountain and be a chef.

730
00:35:45,380 --> 00:35:45,900
Anyway,

731
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:47,380
why are you two looking for me?

732
00:35:48,580 --> 00:35:49,420
For

733
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:50,700
two things.

734
00:35:51,660 --> 00:35:52,420
What is it?

735
00:35:52,940 --> 00:35:53,660
One,

736
00:35:54,180 --> 00:35:55,820
your martial uncle, Lei Yunhe,

737
00:35:56,020 --> 00:35:57,020
visited Mount Wangcheng again.

738
00:35:57,700 --> 00:35:59,340
He made a path with one strike again.

739
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:00,620
The second strike overturned the Qiankun Hall.

740
00:36:00,900 --> 00:36:01,540
And the third strike

741
00:36:01,740 --> 00:36:03,260
seized Zhao Yuzhen's Qingxiao Sword.

742
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:05,540
I heard they fought overnight

743
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:07,220
(and the entire Mount Wangcheng)

744
00:36:07,420 --> 00:36:08,220
(was enveloped)

745
00:36:08,420 --> 00:36:09,140
(by storm and thunder.)

746
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:10,260
(Other than the Six Saints)

747
00:36:10,260 --> 00:36:11,500
(who stayed to spectate,)

748
00:36:11,980 --> 00:36:12,740
others

749
00:36:13,060 --> 00:36:14,380
left the mountain to avoid the crossfire.

750
00:36:15,380 --> 00:36:17,380
And then, your martial uncle
rode his crane and left.

751
00:36:17,820 --> 00:36:18,900
(Zhao Yuzhen also admitted)

752
00:36:19,180 --> 00:36:19,860
(that this time,)

753
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:21,380
(Lei Yunhe did not lose.)

754
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:23,660
That's great.

755
00:36:23,940 --> 00:36:24,900
What's the second thing then?

756
00:36:25,180 --> 00:36:26,100
The second thing

757
00:36:26,340 --> 00:36:27,380
is about a person.

758
00:36:27,940 --> 00:36:28,540
Who?

759
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:30,020
Ye Ruoyi.

760
00:36:31,980 --> 00:36:32,610
Who?

761
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:33,420
I don't know her.

762
00:36:33,700 --> 00:36:34,220
No.

763
00:36:34,620 --> 00:36:35,220
You know her.

764
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:36,260
Not only do you know her,

765
00:36:36,820 --> 00:36:37,740
but she also offered your her handkerchief

766
00:36:38,060 --> 00:36:39,020
(to wipe your nosebleed.)

767
00:36:43,020 --> 00:36:44,660
Why did you bring her up?

768
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:45,980
I didn't ask about her.

769
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:49,780
Okay.

770
00:36:50,180 --> 00:36:50,900
Bye.

771
00:36:52,620 --> 00:36:53,060
Continue, please.

772
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:53,900
Continue, please.

773
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:54,780
Continue, please.

774
00:36:55,340 --> 00:36:56,020
Continue, please.

775
00:36:57,060 --> 00:36:58,660
Ye Ruoyi came to Xueyue City in the same year

776
00:36:58,700 --> 00:36:59,660
as me.

777
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:01,700
She is the daughter of Ye Xiaoying,

778
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:02,780
the Defender-General.

779
00:37:03,540 --> 00:37:04,740
Daughter of a general?

780
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:06,540
Why is she in Xueyue City?

781
00:37:07,020 --> 00:37:07,740
To recuperate.

782
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:10,780
No one knows what sickness she has.

783
00:37:11,340 --> 00:37:12,620
The Third Master is a masterful healer,

784
00:37:13,060 --> 00:37:14,020
but her condition hasn't improved

785
00:37:14,420 --> 00:37:15,460
after many years.

786
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:17,740
The experts from the Directorate of Astronomy

787
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:18,780
have offered their service too,

788
00:37:19,140 --> 00:37:19,940
but to no avail.

789
00:37:20,740 --> 00:37:21,620
It must be

790
00:37:22,220 --> 00:37:23,220
something complicated.

791
00:37:27,220 --> 00:37:28,140
Don't dwell on it.

792
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:29,500
Tell me.

793
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:30,780
Do you want to befriend her?

794
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:34,580
Befriend?

795
00:37:36,180 --> 00:37:37,220
The annual Flora Spectacle of Xueyue City

796
00:37:37,380 --> 00:37:38,460
will take place in three days.

797
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:39,740
All disciples

798
00:37:39,780 --> 00:37:40,500
will attend it.

799
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:41,580
Including

800
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:42,460
the reclusive Ye Ruoyi.

801
00:37:43,540 --> 00:37:44,260
Do you want to be there?

802
00:37:47,180 --> 00:37:48,020
Flora Spectacle...

803
00:37:48,780 --> 00:37:49,900
Will my master be there?

804
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:51,300
Do not

805
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:52,300
tell her about it.

806
00:37:52,860 --> 00:37:53,580
Third Master said

807
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:54,780
anyone can come.

808
00:37:55,060 --> 00:37:56,100
But not Li Hanyi.

809
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,180
Why?

810
00:37:59,380 --> 00:38:00,020
Perhaps because

811
00:38:00,020 --> 00:38:00,860
once she swings her sword...

812
00:38:01,460 --> 00:38:02,020
Go!

813
00:38:06,220 --> 00:38:07,380
All flowers from the Flora Spectacle

814
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:08,580
will be destroyed.

815
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:13,340
What do we do

816
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:14,180
during the spectacle?

817
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:15,140
Do we fight?

818
00:38:15,900 --> 00:38:17,140
The Flora Spectacle is not about violence

819
00:38:17,540 --> 00:38:18,220
but elegance.

820
00:38:18,740 --> 00:38:19,980
Most participants

821
00:38:20,260 --> 00:38:21,340
are from the younger generation.

822
00:38:21,860 --> 00:38:23,500
They recite poems and drink.

823
00:38:24,060 --> 00:38:25,060
It's one of our annual

824
00:38:25,380 --> 00:38:26,820
grand events.

825
00:38:27,180 --> 00:38:29,060
I can drink.

826
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:30,300
But reciting poems?

827
00:38:31,300 --> 00:38:32,380
I can't do that.

828
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:34,380
Besides, we are martial artists.

829
00:38:34,860 --> 00:38:36,060
Reciting poems

830
00:38:36,460 --> 00:38:37,820
feels too...

831
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:39,140
pretentious to me.

832
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:40,020
Why?

833
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:41,500
In Yushi when Wuxin

834
00:38:41,660 --> 00:38:42,780
taught you the fist technique,

835
00:38:42,780 --> 00:38:43,740
he recited a poem too.

836
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,500
Was he being pretentious then?

837
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:48,380
Right.

838
00:38:48,780 --> 00:38:50,940
Wuxin is a spectacular individual.

839
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:54,020
I wonder how he is doing now.

840
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:55,820
He is no easy foe.

841
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,500
He mastered the Six Higher Knowledge Arts

842
00:38:59,100 --> 00:38:59,780
right away

843
00:38:59,780 --> 00:39:01,140
and fought Wushuang from Wushuang City.

844
00:39:04,260 --> 00:39:05,380
It's been a while now,

845
00:39:06,140 --> 00:39:08,020
so he must have improved a lot.

846
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:15,300
Sir.

847
00:39:16,580 --> 00:39:17,500
Duan Chenyi's cronies

848
00:39:17,740 --> 00:39:19,260
and family have been captured.

849
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:20,580
How do we proceed now?

850
00:39:21,260 --> 00:39:22,900
Expel them from Tianwaitian.

851
00:39:23,980 --> 00:39:24,340
Noted.

852
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:26,380
When I traveled

853
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:27,740
with your father in Beili,

854
00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:29,500
I came across this poem.

855
00:39:30,420 --> 00:39:31,100
It reads,

856
00:39:31,820 --> 00:39:33,100
the autumn is upon us,

857
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:34,980
but the moon from my hometown
will always shine the brightest.

858
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:38,700
The moon from my hometown
will always shine the brightest.

859
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:43,100
That's a fine poem.

860
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:45,820
Sir, what is a hometown

861
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:46,620
to you?

862
00:39:47,820 --> 00:39:48,660
Tianwaitian

